items.title: Never forget: 9/11 ceremonies held around MLB
items.summary: The tragic events of Sept. 11, 2001, were remembered across Major League Baseball on Monday, as teams honored those whose lives were lost and affected following the attacks in New York, Washington D.C., and Pennsylvania that changed America forever.
